_sText:
This map is my first full Counter-Strike: Source map. I'm mainly a single player Half-Life 2 mapper, but I decided to make a css map. I feel I was pretty successfully. My friends and I had a lot of fun playing it, and still do, and I hope you do too. Please excuse the bad texture alignment and low detail in some areas, I haven't mapped in a while. Concentrate more on the actual game play itself.

Features: 
Building that can be entered, and has a sniper spot. 
Thunder storm with randomized thunder and lightning.
Big layout.
Very fun with 20+ players/bots.
Dark night time atmosphere.
